1. SCOPE
--------

This repository contains two kinds of materials:

  (A) THE STANDARD — the M3 Framework whitepaper, methodology text,
      diagrams, mappings, matrices in human-readable form (Markdown,
      PDF, images, documentation).

  (B) THE CODE & DATA ARTIFACTS — machine-readable files such as CSV
      annexes, JSON/YAML configurations, policy templates, scripts,
      and any source code in this repository.


